  N5 --> Z1[Outcome: Timely, region-specific adjustments that reduce inventory days and working capital while increasing captured revenue from competitor-driven market shifts; measurable KPIs: lower days-of-inventory, improved regional revenue capture, reduced stock imbalances within the planning horizon.]
  N4 -->|Confidence score below configured thr...| B1[Create Agent Team CWB Action Items for manual review and hold automated writebacks; include diagnostic payload and recommended conservative options]
